    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="6html表格"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#6html表格"></a> 6.HTML表格</h3><p><code>&lt;table&gt;</code>标签定义表格；<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>对应一行；<code>&lt;th&gt;</code>对应一个表头；<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>对应一个单元格–数据容器</p><p>默认格式：<code>&lt;th&gt;</code>元素粗体且居中；<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>左对齐</p><p><code>border</code>属性添加边框–&gt;为表格，表头和表格单元格分别定义边框</p><p><code>border-spacing</code>设置表格边框间距</p><p><code>padding</code>指定单元格空间size</p><p><code>border-collapse</code>：collapse；属性将边框折叠为一个边框</p><p><code>text-align</code>：left；设置左对齐标题</p><p><code>colspan</code>设置单元格跨越多列</p><p><code>rowspan</code>设置单元格跨行</p><p><code>&lt;caption&gt;</code>标签添加表格标题；其后必须紧跟 <code>&lt;table&gt;</code>标签</p><p><mark>特殊样式</mark>表中添加id属性；其后自定义特殊样式</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;table id&#x3D;&quot;t01&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;caption&gt;Monthly savings&lt;&#x2F;caption&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;th&gt;Month&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;th&gt;Savings&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;td&gt;January&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;td&gt;$100&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;td&gt;February&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;td&gt;$50&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;table&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#t01 tr:nth-child(even) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background-color: #eee;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#t01 tr:nth-child(odd) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background-color: #fff;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#t01 th &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  color: white;</span><br><span class="line">  background-color: black;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7html列表"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#7html列表"></a> 7.HTML列表</h3><p>&lt;1&gt;.无序列表：以<code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>开头，每个列表项以 <code>&lt;li&gt;</code>标签开头</p><p><code>list-style-type</code>定义列表项标记样式：disc；circle；square；none</p><p>tips：<code>float：left</code>水平设置列表样式创建导航菜单</p><p>&lt;2&gt;.有序列表：以<code>&lt;ol&gt;</code>开头</p><p><code>type</code>属性定义列表项标记类型：type=“1”/“A”/“a”/“I”/“i”</p><p><code>start</code>属性控制列表从指定数字开始计数：</p><p>&lt;3&gt;.描述列表：以<code>&lt;dl&gt;</code>定义列表，<code>&lt;dt&gt;</code>定义描述词，<code>&lt;dd&gt;</code>描述术语</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">ul &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  list-style-type: none;</span><br><span class="line">  margin: 0;</span><br><span class="line">  padding: 0;</span><br><span class="line">  overflow: hidden;</span><br><span class="line">  background-color: #333333;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">li &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  float: left;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">li a &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  display: block;</span><br><span class="line">  color: white;</span><br><span class="line">  text-align: center;</span><br><span class="line">  padding: 16px;</span><br><span class="line">  text-decoration: none;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">li a:hover &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background-color: #111111;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;ul&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;#home&quot;&gt;Home&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;#news&quot;&gt;News&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;#contact&quot;&gt;Contact&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;#about&quot;&gt;About&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="8html块和内联元素"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#8html块和内联元素"></a> 8.HTML块和内联元素</h3><p>HTML元素的显示值：block和inline</p><p>block：块级元素：总是从新行开始： <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>经常用作容器元素</p><p><img src="E:%5CSoftware-data%5CTypora%5CHTML5%5Cimage-20201031211030661.png" alt="image-20201031211030661" /></p><p>inline：内联元素：仅占用必要的宽度：<code>&lt;span&gt;</code>经常用来标记文本</p><p><img src="E:%5CSoftware-data%5CTypora%5CHTML5%5Cimage-20201031211349687.png" alt="image-20201031211349687" /></p><p><mark>内联元素不能包含块级元素</mark></p><h3 id="9html类属性"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#9html类属性"></a> 9.HTML类属性</h3><p><code>class</code>属性用于指定HTML元素的类</p><p>.类名{ 定义CSS属性 }ps：类名区分大小写</p><p>多个HTML元素可以共享同一类；一个HTML元素可以属于多个类</p><p>JS中可以使用 <code>getElementsByClassName()</code>方法访问具有特定类名的元素</p><p>eg：单击按钮以隐藏所有具有类名称“ city”的元素</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;h2&gt;Use of The class Attribute in JavaScript&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;Click the button to hide all elements with class name &quot;city&quot;:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;button onclick&#x3D;&quot;myFunction()&quot;&gt;Hide elements&lt;&#x2F;button&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;h2 class&#x3D;&quot;city&quot;&gt;London&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;London is the capital of England.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;h2 class&#x3D;&quot;city&quot;&gt;Paris&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;Paris is the capital of France.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;h2 class&#x3D;&quot;city&quot;&gt;Tokyo&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;Tokyo is the capital of Japan.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">function myFunction() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  var x &#x3D; document.getElementsByClassName(&quot;city&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">  for (var i &#x3D; 0; i &lt; x.length; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    x[i].style.display &#x3D; &quot;none&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="10html-id属性"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#10html-id属性"></a> 10.HTML id属性</h3><p><code>id</code>属性用于为HTML元素指定唯一的ID；该ID值在HTML文档中必须唯一</p><p><code>#</code>+id名{  定义CSS属性 }id名区分大小写，至少包含一个字符且不得包含空格</p><p><mark>HTML</mark>书签：允许读者跳转至网页的特定部分</p><pre><code>1. 创建一个含id属性的书签：`&lt;h2 id=&quot;C4&quot;&gt;Chapter 4&lt;/h2&gt;`2. 同一页面跳转：`&lt;a href=&quot;#4&quot;&gt;Jump to Chapter 4&lt;/a&gt;`3. 不同页面跳转：`&lt;a href=&quot;html_demo.html#C4&quot;&gt;Jump to Chapter 4&lt;/a&gt;`</code></pre><p>JS使用 <code>getElementById()</code>方法访问具有特定ID的元素</p><h3 id="11html内联框架"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#11html内联框架"></a> 11.HTML内联框架</h3><p><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code>指定一个内联框架，用于将另一个文档嵌入当前HTML文档中</p><p><code>src</code>属性定义要嵌入页面的URL</p><p><code>&lt;iframe src=&quot;url&quot; title=&quot;description&quot;&gt;</code>：屏幕阅读器通过<code>titile</code>属性读取<code>iframe</code>内容</p><p><code>height</code>和 <code>width</code>属性指定 <code>iframe</code>的尺寸：（可用style属性定义尺寸）</p><p><code>&lt;iframe src=&quot;demo_iframe.htm&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; title=&quot;Iframe Example&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</code></p><p>移除默认边框：<code>style=&quot;border:none;&quot;</code>也可以更改边框大小，样式和颜色</p><p><code>iframe</code>可用作链接的目标框架；该<code>target</code>链接的属性必须引用 <code>name</code>iframe的属性</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;iframe src&#x3D;&quot;demo_iframe.htm&quot; name&#x3D;&quot;iframe_a&quot; title&#x3D;&quot;Iframe Example&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.w3schools.com&quot; target&#x3D;&quot;iframe_a&quot;&gt;W3Schools.com&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
