    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="3html样式-css"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#3html样式-css"></a> 3.HTML样式-CSS</h3><p>CSS：级联样式表–用于格式化网页布局；层叠–继承</p><p>使用方式：</p><p>​内联：使用<code>style</code>HTML元素内在属性；将唯一样式应用于单个属性</p><p>​内部：使用 <code>&lt;head&gt;</code>元素存储 <code>&lt;style&gt;</code>元素控制的其余元素的格式；应用于单个HTML页面</p><p>​外部：使用 <code>&lt;head&gt;</code>元素存储<code>&lt;link&gt;</code>元素控制指定的外部CSS文件的链接</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;link rel&#x3D;&quot;stylesheet&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;style.css&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">body &#123;background-color: powderblue;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">h1 &#123;color: blue;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">p &#123;color: red;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;h1&gt;This is a heading&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;This is a paragraph.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><mark>style.css</mark></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">body &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background-color: powerblue;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">h1 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  color: blue;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">p &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  color: red;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>CSS <code>color</code>属性定义文本颜色</p><p>CSS <code>font-fanmily</code>属性定义文本字体</p><p>CSS <code>font-size</code>属性定义文字大小</p><p>CSS <code>font-align</code>属性定义水平文本对齐方式</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">h1 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">color: blue;</span><br><span class="line">font-family: verdana;</span><br><span class="line">font-size: 300%;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">p &#123;</span><br><span class="line">color: red;</span><br><span class="line">font-family: courier;</span><br><span class="line">font-size: 160%;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;h1&gt;This is a heading&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;This is a paragraph.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>CSS <code>border</code>属性定义HTML元素边框；尺寸+颜色</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  border: 2px solid powderblue;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>CSS <code>padding</code>属性在边框内流出空间</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  border: 2px solid powderblue;</span><br><span class="line">  padding: 30px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>CSS <code>margin</code>属性定义边框外的边距（空格）</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">p &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  border: 2px solid powderblue;</span><br><span class="line">  margin: 50px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>链接到外部CSS</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;link rel&#x3D;&quot;stylesheet&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F; www.w3schools.com&#x2F;html&#x2F;styles.css&gt;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">完整URL链接到样式表</span><br><span class="line">&lt;link rel&#x3D;&quot;stylesheet&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;html&#x2F;styles.css&gt;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">定位到当前网站的html文件夹中的样式表</span><br><span class="line">&lt;link rel&#x3D;&quot;stylesheet&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;styles.css&gt;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">链接到与当前页面同一文件夹中的样式表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4html链接"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#4html链接"></a> 4.HTML链接</h3><p><mark>HTML超链接：<code>&lt;a&gt;</code>元素的 <code>&lt;href&gt;</code>元素指示链接的地址</mark></p><p><code>&lt;target&gt;</code>属性指定在何处打开链接的文档；更改默认显示在当前浏览窗口的设置</p><ul><li><code>_self</code>-默认。在与单击相同的窗口/选项卡中打开文档</li><li><code>_blank</code>-在新窗口/标签中打开文档</li><li><code>_prent</code>-在父框架中打开文档</li><li><code>_top</code>-在整个窗口打开文档</li></ul><p><code>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.w3schools.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Visit W3Schools!&lt;/a&gt;</code></p><p>绝对URL：<code>href</code>中使用完整的Web地址</p><p>相对URKL：不带&quot;<a href="https://xn--www-if2er88z">https://www部分</a>&quot;</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;h2&gt;Absolute URLs&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.w3.org&#x2F;&quot;&gt;W3C&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.google.com&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Google&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;h2&gt;Relative URLs&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;html_images.asp&quot;&gt;HTML Images&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">链接到与当前页面处于同一文件夹中的页面</span><br><span class="line">&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;html&#x2F;default.asp&quot;&gt;HTML tutorial&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">链接到当前网站html文件夹的页面中</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用图像作为链接：将 <code>&lt;img&gt;</code>标签放在标签 <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>内</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;default.asp&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;smiley.gif&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;HTML tutorial&quot; style&#x3D;&quot;width:42px;height:42px;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>链接到邮件地址：<code>mailot</code>在 <code>href</code>属性内使用可创建一个打开邮箱的链接</p><p><code>&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:someone@example.com&quot;&gt;Send email&lt;/a&gt;</code></p><p><mark>按钮作为链接：使用JS</mark></p><p><code>&lt;button onclick=&quot;document.location='default.asp'&quot;&gt;HTML Tutorial&lt;/button&gt;</code></p><p>链接标题：<code>title</code>属性指定有关元素额外（提示）信息</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.w3schools.com&#x2F;html&#x2F;&quot; title&#x3D;&quot;Go to W3Schools HTML section&quot;&gt;Visit our HTML Tutorial&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>链接默认状态下的颜色显示：</p><ul><li>未访问的链接带有下划线且为蓝色</li><li>已访问的链接带有下划线且为紫色</li><li>活动的链接带有下划线且为红色</li></ul><p>创建书签：</p><p>​<code>id</code>属性创建书签；<code>id</code> =“ <em>value</em> ”</p><p>​<code>&lt;h2 id=&quot;C4&quot;&gt;Chapter 4&lt;/h2&gt;</code></p><p>​然后从同一页面添加到书签的链接（跳到第4章）</p><p>​<code>&lt;a href=&quot;#C4&quot;&gt;Jump to Chapter 4&lt;/a&gt;</code></p><p>​从另一个页面添加指向书签的链接；<code>href</code> =“＃<em>value</em>”</p><p>​<code>&lt;a href=&quot;html_demo.html#C4&quot;&gt;Jump to Chapter 4&lt;/a&gt;</code></p><h3 id="5html图片"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#5html图片"></a> 5.HTML图片</h3><p>HTML图像标签：<code>&lt;img&gt;</code>,<code>&lt;map&gt;</code>,<code>&lt;area&gt;</code>,<code>&lt;picture&gt;</code></p><h4 id="1普通图片"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#1普通图片"></a> &lt;1&gt;.普通图片</h4><p><code>&lt;img&gt;</code>标签创建被引用的图像的容纳空间；只包含属性</p><ul><li>src-指定图像的路径；需要确保图像相对于网页处于同一位置</li><li>alt-图像无法加载时指定的替代文字</li></ul><p><code>&lt;img src=&quot;url&quot; alt=&quot;alternatetext&quot;&gt;</code></p><p>图像尺寸</p><ul><li><code>style</code>属性指定图像尺寸</li></ul><p><code>&lt;img src=&quot;img_girl.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Girl in a jacket&quot; style=&quot;width:500px;height:600px;&quot;&gt;</code></p><ul><li><code>width</code>和 <code>height</code>属性</li></ul><p><code>&lt;img src=&quot;img_girl.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Girl in a jacket&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;600&quot;&gt;</code></p><p>另一个文件夹中的图像：<code>src</code>属性包括文件夹名称</p><p>另一台服务器/网站上的图像：<code>src</code>属性指定绝对URL</p><p>用图像做链接：将 <code>&lt;img&gt;</code>标记放在标记 <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>内</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;default.asp&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;smiley.gif&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;HTML tutorial&quot; style&#x3D;&quot;width:42px;height:42px;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>图像浮动：使用CSS的 <code>float</code>属性使图像浮动到文本一侧</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;smiley.gif&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;Smiley face&quot; style&#x3D;&quot;float:right;width:42px;height:42px;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">The image will float to the right of the text.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;smiley.gif&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;Smiley face&quot; style&#x3D;&quot;float:left;width:42px;height:42px;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">The image will float to the left of the text.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2影像图"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#2影像图"></a> &lt;2&gt;.影像图</h4><p><code>&lt;map&gt;</code>标记定义图像映射。图像地点是具有可点区域的图像；用 <code>&lt;area&gt;</code>标签定义区域</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;workplace.jpg&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;Workplace&quot; usemap&#x3D;&quot;#workmap&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;map name&#x3D;&quot;workmap&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;area shape&#x3D;&quot;rect&quot; coords&#x3D;&quot;34,44,270,350&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;Computer&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;computer.htm&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;area shape&#x3D;&quot;rect&quot; coords&#x3D;&quot;290,172,333,250&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;Phone&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;phone.htm&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;area shape&#x3D;&quot;circle&quot; coords&#x3D;&quot;337,300,44&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;Coffee&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;coffee.htm&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;map&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><mark>影像图工作原理</mark></p><ul><li><p>使用 <code>&lt;img&gt;</code>标签插入图像，唯一区别为必须添加 <code>usemap</code>属性</p><p><code>&lt;img src=&quot;workplace.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Workplace&quot; usemap=&quot;#workmap&quot;&gt;</code></p><p><code>#</code>号用于创建图像和图像地图之间的关系</p></li><li><p>添加一个 <code>&lt;map&gt;</code>元素，用于创建图像映射且通过所需要的链接到图像属性</p><p><code>&lt;map name=&quot;workmap&quot;&gt;</code><code>name</code>属性值对应于<code>usemap</code>属性</p></li><li><p>通过 <code>&lt;area&gt;</code>添加可点击区域</p></li><li><p>定义形状（需要指定坐标点）</p><ul><li><code>rect</code>-定义一个矩形区域；<code>shape=&quot;rect&quot;</code>成对存在对应x和y轴</li><li><code>circle</code>-定义一个圆形区域；<code>shape=&quot;circle&quot;</code>指定圆心坐标和半径</li><li><code>poly</code>-定义一个多边形区域；<code>Shape =“ poly”</code>包含多边形所有边缘坐标点</li><li><code>default</code>-定义整个区域</li></ul><p><code>&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;34, 44, 270, 350&quot; href=&quot;computer.htm&quot;&gt;</code></p><p><code>&lt;area shape=&quot;circle&quot; coords=&quot;337, 300, 44&quot; href=&quot;coffee.htm&quot;&gt;</code></p></li></ul><p>影像图可点击区域可以出发JS函数：<code>click</code>向 <code>&lt;area&gt;</code>元素添加事件执行JS函数</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;map name&#x3D;&quot;workmap&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;area shape&#x3D;&quot;circle&quot; coords&#x3D;&quot;337,300,44&quot; onclick&#x3D;&quot;myFunction()&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;map&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">function myFunction() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  alert(&quot;You clicked the coffee cup!&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">当单击区域时，我们使用onclick属性执行JavaScript函数</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3html背景图"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#3html背景图"></a> &lt;3&gt;<mark>HTML背景图</mark></h4><ul><li>使用 <code>style</code>属性和CSS <code>background-image</code>属性</li></ul><p><code>&lt;div style=&quot;background-image: url('img_girl.jpg');&quot;&gt;</code></p><ul><li>在<code>&lt;style&gt;</code>元素的 <code>&lt;head&gt;</code>部分指定背景图片</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">div &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background-image: url(&#39;img_girl.jpg&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>为整个页面添加背景图片；在 <code>&lt;body&gt;</code>元素上指定背景图像</p></li><li><p>为避免背景图像重复出现，请将<code>background-repeat</code>属性设置为<code>no-repeat</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">body &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background-image: url(&#39;img_girl.jpg&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">  background-repeat: no-repeat</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>背景封面：</p><p>​background-size: cover</p><p>​如果希望背景图像覆盖整个元素，则可以将<code>background-size</code>属性设置为 <code>cover.</code></p><p>​另外，要确保始终覆盖整个元素，请将<code>background-attachment</code>属性设置 为<code>fixed:</code>(图像维持原始比例)</p><p>​如果要拉伸背景图像以适合整个元素，可以将<code>background-size</code>属性设置为 <code>100% 100%</code>：</p><h4 id="4图片元素"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#4图片元素"></a> &lt;4&gt;图片元素</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;picture&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;source media&#x3D;&quot;(min-width: 650px)&quot; srcset&#x3D;&quot;img_food.jpg&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;source media&#x3D;&quot;(min-width: 465px)&quot; srcset&#x3D;&quot;img_car.jpg&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;img_girl.jpg&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;picture&gt;</span><br><span class="line"># 针对不同的屏幕尺寸显示不同的图像</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>&lt;source&gt;</code>元素含有 <code>media</code>属性定义何时最适合图像；<code>&lt;img&gt;</code>元素作为备用元素</p><p>浏览器或设备使用第一种识别的图像格式</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;picture&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;source srcset&#x3D;&quot;img_avatar.png&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;source srcset&#x3D;&quot;img_girl.jpg&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;img_beatles.gif&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;Beatles&quot; style&#x3D;&quot;width:auto;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;picture&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
