    <title>HTML5使用</title>
    <link href="https://0rigindu.top/posts/5d59bf6f.html"/>
    <id>https://0rigindu.top/posts/5d59bf6f.html</id>
    <published>2020-11-14T00:24:00.460Z</published>
    <updated>2020-12-16T00:44:43.868Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>（本文以及同系列文章为博主在<a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/index.html">w3school</a>学习HTML的笔记，代码多源于原教程）</p></blockquote><h2 id="一-html的基础"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#一-html的基础"></a> 一· HTML的基础</h2><h3 id="1-html框架"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#1-html框架"></a> 1. html框架</h3><p><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code>声明html5文档类型</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="meta-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>Page Title<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>This is a Heading<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>This is a paragraph.<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-html基础"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#2-html基础"></a> 2. HTML基础</h3><h4 id="1-html元素"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#1-html元素"></a> &lt;1&gt; HTML元素</h4><p><code>&lt;tagname&gt;</code>内容…<code>&lt;/tagname&gt;</code> HTML元素包括从开始标记到结束标记所有内容</p><p><mark>HTML元素嵌套</mark> HTML文档均由嵌套的HTML元素组成</p><p><code>&lt;html&gt;</code>元件是HTML页面的根元素</p><p><code>&lt;head&gt;</code>元素包含HTML页面的元信息</p><p><code>&lt;title&gt;</code>元素指定用于HTML页面的标题（浏览器标题栏）</p><p><code>&lt;body&gt;</code>元素包含所有可见内容</p><p><code>&lt;h1&gt; -- &lt;h6&gt;</code>元素定义标题；重要性减弱；可以用<code>style</code>和CSS的<code>font-size</code>指定标题大小</p><p><code>&lt;h1 style=&quot;font-size:60px;&quot;&gt;Heading 1&lt;/h1&gt;</code></p><p><code>&lt;a&gt;</code>元素定义HTML链接 ；<code>href(属性)</code>= 链接目的地</p><p><code>&lt;a href='https://www.W3Schools.com'&gt;This is a link&lt;/a&gt;</code></p><p><code>&lt;img&gt;</code>标签定义HTML图像；源文件（<code>src</code>），替代文本（<code>alt</code>）<code>wedith</code>和 <code>&lt;height&gt;</code>作为属性提供</p><p><code>&lt;img src=&quot;W3Schools.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;W3School.com&quot; width=&quot;104&quot; height=&quot;142&quot;&gt;</code></p><p><code>&lt;p&gt;</code>元素定义段落；</p><p><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code>标签显示为一条水平线（分离符）；</p><p><code>&lt;br&gt;</code> 空元素==换行符/空格（没有结束标签）</p><p><code>&lt;pre&gt;</code>元素定义预格式化文本；字体有固定宽度且保留空格和换行符</p><p><mark>文本格式元素</mark></p><p><code>&lt;b&gt;</code>粗体；<code>&lt;strong&gt;</code>重要（粗体）文字；<code>&lt;i&gt;</code>斜体；<code>&lt;em&gt;</code>强调文本（斜体）；<code>&lt;mark&gt;</code>标记文字；<code>&lt;small&gt;</code>；<code>&lt;del&gt;</code>删除的文字；<code>&lt;ins&gt;</code>插入文字（下划线）；<code>&lt;sub&gt;</code>下标文字；<code>&lt;sup&gt;</code>上标文字</p><p><code>&lt;p&gt;My favorite color is &lt;del&gt;blue&lt;/del&gt; &lt;ins&gt;red&lt;/ins&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</code></p><p><mark>引用元素</mark></p><p><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code>元素定义引用另一个来源的部分；通常缩进</p><p><code>&lt;q&gt;</code>标记定义短引号；<code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code>标签定义缩写；鼠标悬停显示；</p><p><code>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;abbr title=&quot;World Health Organization&quot;&gt;WHO&lt;/abbr&gt; was founded in 1948.&lt;/p&gt;</code></p><p><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code>标签定义作品标题（斜体）</p><p><code>&lt;p&gt;&lt;cite&gt;The Scream&lt;/cite&gt; by Edvard Munch. Painted in 1893.&lt;/p&gt;</code></p><p><code>&lt;bod&gt;</code>标签用于覆盖当前文本方向；<code>lrt</code>从左到右；<code>rtl</code>从右到左</p><p><code>&lt;bdo dir=&quot;rtl&quot;&gt;This line will be written from right to left&lt;/bdo&gt;</code></p><p><code>&lt;address&gt;</code>标记定义所有者联系信息（斜体，其前后自动添加换行符）</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;address&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Written by John Doe.&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Visit us at:&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Example.com&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Box 564, Disneyland&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class="line">USA</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;address&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>&lt;!-- Write your comments here --&gt;</code>注释标签</p><h4 id="2-html属性"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#2-html属性"></a> &lt;2&gt; HTML属性</h4><p>属性在开始标记中指定；通常以名称/值对的形式出现</p><p><code>lang</code>属性声明网页的语言</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="meta-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">&quot;en&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>href</code>属性为 <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>标签定义的超链接；指定链接页面的URL</p><p><code>&lt;a href='https://www.W3Schools.com'&gt;Visit W3School&lt;/a&gt;</code></p><p><code>src</code>属性为 <code>&lt;img&gt;</code>标签指定的图像路径；<code>alt</code>属性提供图像备用文本；<code>width</code>和 <code>height</code>指定图像参数</p><p><code>&lt;img src=&quot;img_girl.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Girl with a jacket&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;600&quot;&gt;</code> 相对URL链接到网站内托管的图像。</p><p><code>style</code>属性向元素添加样式；<code>&lt;tagname style=&quot;property:value;&quot;&gt;</code></p><p><code>background-color</code>背景色；<code>color</code>字体颜色；<code>font-family</code>字体；<code>font-size</code>文本大小；<code>text-align</code>文本水平对齐；</p><p><code>&lt;p style=&quot;background-color:powderblue;font-family:verdana;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;This is a paragraph.&lt;/p&gt;</code></p><p><mark>HTML文档设置颜色方式：</mark></p><p><mark>RGB值（红，绿，蓝）灰色阴影为三个相等参数；</mark></p><p><mark>HEX值（#红绿蓝–十六进制值 00-ff）</mark></p><p><mark>HSL值（色相 0-360 红-绿-蓝均分，饱和度 0为灰色阴影–1为纯色，亮度 0为黑色–1为白色）</mark></p><p>通常通过将色调和饱和度设置为0来定义灰色阴影，并将亮度从0％调整为100％，以获得更深/更浅的阴影</p><p><mark>RGBA值和HSLA值会为该颜色添加一个Alpha通道；作为不透明度的参数</mark></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;h1 style&#x3D;&quot;background-color:rgb(255, 99, 71);&quot;&gt;rgb(255, 99, 71)&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;h1 style&#x3D;&quot;background-color:#ff6347;&quot;&gt;#ff6347&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;h1 style&#x3D;&quot;background-color:hsl(9, 100%, 64%);&quot;&gt;hsl(9, 100%, 64%)&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;h1 style&#x3D;&quot;background-color:rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.5);&quot;&gt;rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.5)&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;h1 style&#x3D;&quot;background-color:hsla(9, 100%, 64%, 0.5);&quot;&gt;hsla(9, 100%, 64%, 0.5)&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>title</code>定义有关元素的额外信息（备注，鼠标悬停时显示）</p><p><code>&lt;p title=&quot;I'am a tooltip&quot;&gt;This is a paragraph.&lt;/p&gt;</code></p><p>ps：属性名称小写；&quot;<mark>属性值引用</mark>&quot;时根据需求单双引号混用</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
